org.openehealth.ipf.commons.ihe.xds.core.metadata

Class Address

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openehealth.ipf.commons.ihe.xds.core.metadata.Hl7v2Based<ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v25.datatype.XAD>
      • org.openehealth.ipf.commons.ihe.xds.core.metadata.Address
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Address
extends Hl7v2Based<ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v25.datatype.XAD>
    Represents the address of a patient.

    This class contains a subset of the fields from the HL7v2.5 XAD data type.

    All members of this class are allowed to be null. When transforming to HL7 this indicates that the values are empty. Trailing empty values are removed from the HL7 string.

    Author:
    Jens Riemschneider, Dmytro Rud
